WEBVTT

00:06:29.556 --> 00:06:32.024
(Laughter)

00:06:33.014 --> 00:06:34.443
To sustain this effort,

00:06:34.467 --> 00:06:38.469
we've installed 10 sanitary napkin
dispensers in several schools.

00:06:39.127 --> 00:06:42.595
Gradually, people's mindsets are changing.

00:06:43.267 --> 00:06:45.973
But does change come so easily?

00:06:46.932 --> 00:06:48.650
At a school for the underprivileged,

00:06:48.674 --> 00:06:51.452
we encountered a girl who had just
got her first period

00:06:51.476 --> 00:06:54.176
but wasn't wearing anything
to absorb the flow.

00:06:54.731 --> 00:06:56.746
Imagine being her,

00:06:56.770 --> 00:07:00.014
sitting in class feeling
embarrassed and uncomfortable,